 《奥本海默》再创票房纪录https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-imax-box-office-record-3533160?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=oppenheimer-imax-box-office-recordAlex Berry Tue, 07 Nov 2023 19:48:44 +0000 Film NewsNewsBarbie https://www.nme.com/?p=3533160 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲 饰 奥本海默" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>克里斯托弗·诺兰的传记片成为票房最高的 IMAX 电影之一</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-imax-box-office-record-3533160">《奥本海默》的帖子打破了另一项票房纪录，</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲 饰 奥本海默" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>奥本海默</em></a>重返 IMAX 并打破了新的票房纪录。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">《奥本海默》评论：克里斯托弗·诺兰令人兴奋的传记片像一颗炸弹一样击中大脑</a></li></ul><p>克里斯托弗·诺兰的电影首次在电影院上映，成为 2023 年票房第三高的电影，仅次于<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>《芭比娃娃》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/super-mario-bros-movie-review-chris-pratt-3425797"><em>《超级马里奥兄弟电影》</em></a> 。</p><p>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">希里安·墨菲</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-downey-jr">小罗伯特·唐尼</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emily-blunt">艾米莉·布朗特</a>主演的<em>奥本海默</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-is-coming-back-to-imax-cinemas-soon-3527904">于上周四重返世界各地的 IMAX 影院</a>，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/when-is-oppenheimer-available-to-stream-release-date-3493055">11 月 22 日国内上映</a>之前重新放映了这部广受好评的传记片一周。 </p><figure id="attachment_3533171" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3533171" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3533171" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-and-Christopher-Nolan.jpg" alt="希里安·墨菲和克里斯托弗·诺兰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-and-Christopher-Nolan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-and-Christopher-Nolan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-and-Christopher-Nolan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-and-Christopher-Nolan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-and-Christopher-Nolan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Cillian-Murphy-and-Christopher-Nolan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3533171" class="wp-caption-text">从左到右：希里安·墨菲（饰演 J·罗伯特·奥本海默）和编剧、导演兼制片人克里斯托弗·诺兰在《奥本海默》片场。信用：环球</figcaption></figure><p>根据<em><a href="https://collider.com/oppenheimer-global-imax-box-office-184-million/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Collider 的数据</a></em>，在回归的周末，该片又额外赚了 55 万美元，使该片 IMAX 全球票房总收入达到 1.84 亿美元。</p><p>根据<a href="https://screenrant.com/oppenheimer-box-office-record-imax-rerelease/"><em>ScreenRant 的数据</em></a>，在国际重新上映后，该片在 IMAX 的票房收入现已达到 9640 万美元。因此， <em>《奥本海默》</em>成为国际 IMAX 史上票房收入第四高的影片。它将电影排在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/avatar-the-way-of-water-review-3366050"><em>《阿凡达：水之道》</em></a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/avengers-endgame-review-2479864"><em>《复仇者联盟：终局之战</em></a>》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avatar"><em>《阿凡达》</em></a>之后。</p><p>得益于<em>奥本海默</em>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/mission-impossible-dead-reckoning-part-1-review-tom-cruise-3464795">《碟中谍6：航位推测第一部》，该公司的收入大幅增长了 50% 以上，之后又重返</a>IMAX 影院。</em></p><p>这部电影采用高分辨率 IMAX 70 毫米胶片摄影机拍摄，全球票房即将突破 10 亿美元大关。诺兰本人曾表示，IMAX 格式是观看奥本海默<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christopher-nolan-best-seats-watch-movie-theatre-3451596">的“最佳体验”</a> 。</p><p>尽管他强调了电影数字化版本的工作，但他补充道：“这是拍摄 IMAX 电影的令人兴奋的事情：当您扫描数字格式时，您正在使用绝对最好的图像。获得。这非常适合激光投影仪等新的投影仪格式。”</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在一篇<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">五星级评论</a>中写道：“奥本海默是成人电影制作领域的一项里程碑式的成就。”</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-passes-bohemian-rhapsody-most-successful-biopic-ever-3499601"><em>奥本海默</em>刚刚超越<em>波西米亚狂想曲</em></a>，成为有史以来票房最高的传记片。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-imax-box-office-record-3533160">《奥本海默》的帖子打破了另一项票房纪录，</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布。</p> ;
