 《虎王》中的安特尔博士承认贩卖野生动物和洗钱罪https://www.nme.com/news/tv/tiger-king-star-doc-antle-pleads-guilty-wildlife-trafficking-money-laundering-3533115?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tiger-king-star-安特尔博士认罪贩卖野生动物洗钱Adam StarkeyTue, 07 Nov 2023 17:12:34 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3533115 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安特尔博士" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>安特尔因违反保护濒危动物的法律而面临最高五年的监禁</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/tiger-king-star-doc-antle-pleads-guilty-wildlife-trafficking-money-laundering-3533115">《虎王》中的安特尔博士承认贩卖野生动物和洗钱罪的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安特尔博士" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>剧集<em>《虎王》</em>中的 Bhagavan “Doc” Antle 承认犯有野生动物贩运和洗钱罪。</p><p>安特尔是极度濒危和稀有物种研究所 (TIGERS) 的所有者，该研究所也称为南卡罗来纳州默特尔比奇野生动物园。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/doc-antle-owner-myrtle-beach-safari-pleads-guilty-federal-wildlife-trafficking-and-money" target="_blank" rel="noopener">美国司法部</a>称，安特尔指挥出售或购买两只狮子幼崽、两只老虎、两只猎豹幼崽和一只幼崽，共谋违反了《雷斯法案》——该法案禁止非法贩运受《濒危物种法案》保护的野生动物。 2018年9月至2020年5月期间的黑猩猩。</p><p>据称，安特尔使用大笔现金支付来隐藏交易并伪造文件。据说他还要求通过他的非营利组织稀有物种基金为濒临灭绝的物种支付费用，这样它们就可以表现为“捐赠”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3533121" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3533121" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3533121" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-main.jpg" alt="安特尔博士" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Doc-Antle-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3533121" class="wp-caption-text">安特尔博士。图片来源：Jonathan Wiggs/《波士顿环球报》来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>检察官称，2022 年 2 月至 4 月期间，安特尔和一名同谋使用他们认为是通过运输和窝藏非法移民获得的现金进行洗钱。</p><p>对于每项罪名，安特尔将面临最高五年的监禁、最高 25 万美元的罚款和三年的监管释放。他的认罪被美国地区法官约瑟夫道森三世接受，他将在审查安特尔的量刑报告后对他进行宣判。</p><p> “被告自称是自然资源保护主义者，但却屡次违反保护濒危动物的法律，然后试图掩盖这些违法行为，”司法部环境和自然资源司助理总检察长托德·金说。</p><p> “这次起诉表明了我们打击非法贩运的承诺，非法贩运威胁着濒危动物的生存。”</p><p>安特尔此前曾于六月因贩运野生动物罪被定罪。陪审团宣判他五项虐待动物罪名无罪。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/tiger-king-star-doc-antle-pleads-guilty-wildlife-trafficking-money-laundering-3533115">《虎王》中的安特尔博士承认贩卖野生动物和洗钱罪的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
